==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: carbon-14
<hw>carbon-14</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a radioactive isotope of carbon
with a half-life of 5730 years. It occurs naturally in minute
quantities, and is used as the basis for <er>radiocarbon
dating</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> radiocarbon, carbon 14.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Carbonaceous</ent>⟦br⟧
